      </div>
      <div class="toggle-row">
        <div class="toggle-info">
          <h4>Show Explanations in Review</h4>
          <p>After test, show the explanation for each wrong answer in the review section.</p>
        </div>
        <label class="toggle"><input type="checkbox" id="cfg-explain" checked><span class="toggle-slider"></span></label>
      </div>
      <div class="toggle-row">
        <div class="toggle-info">
          <h4>Auto-advance on Single-Answer Questions</h4>
          <p>Automatically go to next question after selecting one answer on single-correct questions.</p>
