      <p style="font-size:12px;color:#3b82f6;margin:0 0 14px;">Used for OTP delivery and test report emails. Get credentials from <a href="https://emailjs.com" target="_blank" style="color:#1d4ed8;">emailjs.com</a> (free: 200 emails/month).</p>
      <div class="form-grid">
