<div class="tab-section" id="tab-courses">
  <div class="panel">
    <div class="panel-title"><span>📚</span> Questions by Course / Category</div>
    <p style="font-size:13px;color:#64748b;margin:0 0 16px;">Each question belongs to a category that maps to a course. The test draws questions from all active categories equally when shuffling.</p>
    <div id="course-map-list">
      <div style="text-align:center;padding:30px;color:#94a3b8;">Loading…</div>
    </div>
