        <li>If the selected course has fewer than 50 questions, remaining slots are filled from <strong>General IT</strong> questions</li>
        <li>If no course is selected, questions are pulled randomly across <strong>all active categories</strong></li>
        <li>Scholarship discounts apply regardless of which course category was tested</li>
